this is a django project that contains the code that runs http://hack.markng.co.uk/.

The latest version of this can be found at http://github.com/markng/hacksforhacks/tree/master .

The intention of this set of hacks is to show practical examples of ways in which journalists could use python and django in order to quickly work with data.

Everything in this project is released into the Public Domain unless stated otherwise, and comes with no warranty, explicit or implied.